WEBVTT

00:06:59.470 --> 00:07:01.994
And then, of course,
it's used by governments.

00:07:02.018 --> 00:07:05.239
And there's obviously
a sexual violence component to this,

00:07:05.263 --> 00:07:08.964
which is that this kind of surveillance
can be used most effectively

00:07:08.988 --> 00:07:15.791
against women and other people
who can be shamed in our society.

00:07:16.417 --> 00:07:18.525
Even if you think
you have nothing to hide,

00:07:18.549 --> 00:07:23.107
at the very least, if you have
children, teenagers in your lives,

00:07:23.131 --> 00:07:26.141
make sure you put a sticker
on their camera and protect them.

00:07:26.165 --> 00:07:28.159
HW: Wow. Thank you so much.
CS: Thank you.

00:07:28.183 --> 00:07:29.334
HW: Thanks, Chris.

00:07:29.358 --> 00:07:31.830
(Applause)